title: Tribal Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Opened in June 2012, this is their second LA location; the other is at 1651 W Temple St, historic Filipino Town area / Echo Park of Los Angeles. The veggie friendly menu includes green smoothies, hearty salads and sandwiches. Colorful, hippie bohemian decor with artworks on the walls. Host open mic and events. Its other location at 3253 Beverly Blvd, Silver Lake had shut down in 2013.
